Class Generic_Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.core.Generic_Object
      • uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.time.Generic_YearMonth
        • uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.time.Generic_Date
          • uk.ac.leeds.ccg.agdt.generic.time.Generic_Time
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Generic_YearMonth>
    public class Generic_Time
extends Generic_Date
    Holds a reference to a LocalDateTime and provides methods to compare and process times. It should not be confused with the identically named Generic_Time class.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Andy Turner
